(EW.com) -- "Facts of Life" star and "Survivor" schemer Lisa Whelchel has West Nile virus.

The 49-year-old actress tweeted her condition, writing, "Dr. just called with blood test results...I have West Nile. Ugh. I'm fine, just tired. Takes a year to recover."

It's unknown where she contracted the illness, which can be spread by mosquitoes.

